A qualified relation between a CompositionStatement (about a whole) and ONE of its constituents. Carries the measured amount (ceon:hasQuantityInterval) and per-edge metadata (contentHash, quality) for that single part, and points at the shared part individual via futuram:refersTo. Deliberately NOT a ceon:Constituent: CEON's Constituent is a non-recursive leaf (not a PhysicalObject, cannot itself have constituents), whereas the part a PartRelation refers to (e.g. a motor) is a full PhysicalObject that is a whole elsewhere in the recursive composition tree. The qualified relation lets the same shared part carry per-edge data without being collapsed into the edge.:

